name: PZBGIS.SENIORS_CMTY
description: This geodataset provides the geographic boundaries of Senior communities in Palm Beach County determined to house a population of seniors where the 2000 census shows 75% or greater are aged 55 or over. Retirement and rest homes are included as determined by the Property Appraiser's property use. The entire county is represented, whether in the unincorporated areas or within municipal boundaries
